Navigate with the left stick and you can go to the SHIELD store, a front-end for SHIELD-enabled titles on the Play Store. (Don't worry, you still buy and play them through the Play Store, and the purchases are linked to your Google Account.) This is a great way to get a quick look at some of the games that will work best on your hardware. Then there's the much-lauded PC game streaming, which I'll touch on later.
